<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="explicit-adj">explicit <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪk'splɪsɪt/    美 /ɪk'splɪsɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>清楚的；明确的；直言的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>be <strong>explicit about</strong> an affair
对某事件态度鲜明</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The teacher's explicit explanation left the students no confusion over that abstract theory.
老师清晰的解释使学生对那个抽象的理论没有任何疑惑。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His comprehensive surveys have provided the most explicit statements of how, and on what basis, data are collected.
他的综合调查非常清楚地说明了应该以什么样的方式、以什么为基础收集数据。</p><footer>2016 江苏</footer></div></div>